Task-Per-Derivative: 1
Task-Section: user
Task-Description: Vinux desktop DVD
Task-Extended-Description: This task provides the extra packages installed on the Vinux desktop DVD image, above and beyond those included on the Vinux CD image. It is neither useful nor recommended to install this task in other environments.
Task-Key: libreoffice-writer
Task-Seeds: desktop-common desktop

